# Claude Code Rules for AI Reservations

## Project Structure
- All source code is in `src/` directory
- Use `@/` for imports (maps to `src/`)
- Feature-based organization under `src/modules/`
- Shared components in `src/shared/`
- App Router in `src/app/`

## Code Standards
- 100% TypeScript (no .js files)
- Use `"use client"` directive when needed
- Extract logic into custom hooks
- Follow RULES.md guidelines

## Import Paths
Always use `@/` alias:
- `@/shared/components/ui/button`
- `@/modules/dashboard/components/DashboardContainer`
- `@/lib/utils`
- `@/providers/ConvexClientProvider`

